        "subject": "LU-1497 client: SLES11 SP0 client build is broken.",
        "message": "LU-1497 client: SLES11 SP0 client build is broken.\n\nWith the addition of client improvements new linux kernel\napis are exposed to the llite layer. Those apis can be\nmissing or have a different format in earlier kernels.\nThis is the case for SLES11 SP0 clients whose\nvma handling is different than later kernel version.\nThis patch fixes those issues.\n\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: Id429a7fc5a16dafecba4ac074b7f815811e1c611\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_2"
    }
